datasets.name: b2c73431
queryLines:
SELECT
    year,
    month,
    make_date(year, month, day) AS trip_date,
    time_bucket,
    vendor_id,

    CASE
        WHEN :metric_selector = 'revenue'
            THEN SUM(total_amount)

        WHEN :metric_selector = 'distance'
            THEN SUM(trip_distance)

        WHEN :metric_selector = 'passengers'
            THEN SUM(passenger_count)

        WHEN :metric_selector = 'trips'
            THEN COUNT(*)
    END AS selected_metric

FROM bi_taxi_secure
GROUP BY year, month, trip_date, time_bucket, vendor_id
ORDER BY trip_date;

datasets.name: 1bc576cf
queryLines:
SELECT *
FROM (

    SELECT
        year,
        month,
        make_date(year, month, day) AS trip_date,
        vendor_id,
        'revenue' AS metric_type,
        SUM(total_amount) AS metric_value
    FROM bi_taxi_secure
    GROUP BY year, month, make_date(year, month, day), vendor_id

    UNION ALL

    SELECT
        year,
        month,
        make_date(year, month, day),
        vendor_id,
        'distance',
        SUM(trip_distance)
    FROM bi_taxi_secure
    GROUP BY year, month, make_date(year, month, day), vendor_id

    UNION ALL

    SELECT
        year,
        month,
        make_date(year, month, day),
        vendor_id,
        'passengers',
        SUM(passenger_count)
    FROM bi_taxi_secure
    GROUP BY year, month, make_date(year, month, day), vendor_id

    UNION ALL

    SELECT
        year,
        month,
        make_date(year, month, day),
        vendor_id,
        'trips',
        COUNT(*)
    FROM bi_taxi_secure
    GROUP BY year, month, make_date(year, month, day), vendor_id

) t

WHERE metric_type = :metric_selector
ORDER BY trip_date;

datasets.name: 5fc18ac7
queryLines:
WITH base AS (
  SELECT
    year,
    month,
    make_date(year,month,day) AS trip_date,
    vendor_id,

    SUM(fare_amount) AS fare,
    SUM(tip_amount) AS tip,
    SUM(tolls_amount) AS tolls,
    SUM(extra) AS extra,
    SUM(mta_tax) AS mta_tax,
    SUM(improvement_surcharge) AS improvement

  FROM bi_taxi_secure
  GROUP BY
    year,
    month,
    make_date(year,month,day),
    vendor_id
)

SELECT year,month,trip_date,vendor_id,'Fare' AS fare_type,fare AS amount FROM base
UNION ALL
SELECT year,month,trip_date,vendor_id,'Tip',tip FROM base
UNION ALL
SELECT year,month,trip_date,vendor_id,'Tolls',tolls FROM base
UNION ALL
SELECT year,month,trip_date,vendor_id,'Extra',extra FROM base
UNION ALL
SELECT year,month,trip_date,vendor_id,'MTA Tax',mta_tax FROM base
UNION ALL
SELECT year,month,trip_date,vendor_id,'Improvement Surcharge',improvement FROM base;

datasets.name: 5867b2c1
queryLines:
WITH base AS (
  SELECT
      year,
      month,
      make_date(year,month,day) AS trip_date,
      vendor_id,

      SUM(total_amount) AS revenue,
      SUM(trip_distance) AS distance,
      COUNT(*) AS trips,
      SUM(passenger_count) AS passengers

  FROM bi_taxi_secure
  GROUP BY
      year,
      month,
      make_date(year,month,day),
      vendor_id
),

unpivoted AS (
  SELECT year,month,trip_date,vendor_id,'Revenue' AS metric_type,revenue AS metric_value FROM base
  UNION ALL
  SELECT year,month,trip_date,vendor_id,'Distance',distance FROM base
  UNION ALL
  SELECT year,month,trip_date,vendor_id,'Trips',trips FROM base
  UNION ALL
  SELECT year,month,trip_date,vendor_id,'Passengers',passengers FROM base
)

SELECT
    year,
    month,
    trip_date,
    vendor_id,
    metric_type,
    metric_value,

    -- normalization per metric_type (across vendors)
    (metric_value - MIN(metric_value) OVER (PARTITION BY metric_type))
    /
    NULLIF(
        MAX(metric_value) OVER (PARTITION BY metric_type)
        - MIN(metric_value) OVER (PARTITION BY metric_type),
        0
    ) AS heat_value

FROM unpivoted
ORDER BY trip_date;

datasets.name: 670756aa
queryLines:
WITH base AS (
  SELECT
    year,
    month,
    make_date(year, month, day) AS trip_date,

    vendor_id,

    ROUND(pickup_latitude,3)  AS pickup_lat,
    ROUND(pickup_longitude,3) AS pickup_lon,

    ROUND(dropoff_latitude,3)  AS dropoff_lat,
    ROUND(dropoff_longitude,3) AS dropoff_lon,

    COUNT(*) AS trip_count,
    SUM(total_amount) AS revenue

  FROM powerbi_poc.poc_schema.bi_taxi_secure

  GROUP BY
    year,
    month,
    make_date(year, month, day),
    vendor_id,
    ROUND(pickup_latitude,3),
    ROUND(pickup_longitude,3),
    ROUND(dropoff_latitude,3),
    ROUND(dropoff_longitude,3)
)

SELECT *,
  CASE
    WHEN :kpi_selector='trips' THEN trip_count
    WHEN :kpi_selector='revenue' THEN revenue
  END AS selected_kpi
FROM base;

datasets.name: 7c47bc81
queryLines:
WITH monthly AS (
  SELECT
      year,
      month,
      vendor_id,

      SUM(total_amount)    AS revenue,
      COUNT(*)             AS trips,
      SUM(trip_distance)   AS distance,
      SUM(passenger_count) AS passengers

  FROM bi_taxi_secure
  GROUP BY year, month, vendor_id
),

calc AS (
  SELECT *,
      LAG(revenue) OVER (PARTITION BY vendor_id ORDER BY year,month) AS prev_revenue,
      LAG(trips) OVER (PARTITION BY vendor_id ORDER BY year,month) AS prev_trips,
      LAG(distance) OVER (PARTITION BY vendor_id ORDER BY year,month) AS prev_distance,
      LAG(passengers) OVER (PARTITION BY vendor_id ORDER BY year,month) AS prev_passengers
  FROM monthly
)

SELECT
  vendor_id,
  year,
  month,

  -- current
  revenue,
  trips,
  distance,
  passengers,

  -- previous
  prev_revenue,
  prev_trips,
  prev_distance,
  prev_passengers

FROM calc;
